FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: What types of recipes can I find on this app?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Our app offers a wide variety of recipes, from quick weeknight dinners to gourmet cuisine, covering all dietary preferences and skill levels.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: Can I create and save my own meal plans?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: Absolutely! You can easily create, customize, and save meal plans tailored to your preferences and dietary needs.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: Is there a grocery list feature?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Yes, our app automatically generates grocery lists based on your selected recipes and meal plans, making shopping a breeze.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: Can I adjust serving sizes for recipes?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Certainly! You can easily scale recipes up or down to match your desired number of servings, and ingredient quantities will adjust accordingly.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: Are there options for dietary restrictions?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: Yes, we cater to various dietary needs including vegetarian, vegan, gluten-free, and more. You can filter recipes based on your specific requirements.
PLACEHOLDER_FAQ_TITLE: Frequently Asked Questions About Our Food App
ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: What types of cuisine does your app cover?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Our app covers a wide variety of cuisines from around the world, including Italian, Chinese, Mexican, Indian, and many more. We're constantly expanding our database to include new and exciting food options.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_2: Can I use the app to order food for delivery?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Yes! Our app allows you to browse menus from local restaurants and place orders for delivery or pickup. We partner with numerous establishments to ensure a seamless ordering experience.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: Are there any special features for dietary restrictions?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Absolutely! Our app includes filters for various dietary needs such as vegetarian, vegan, gluten-free, and allergen-free options. You can easily customize your search to find meals that suit your specific requirements.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: How does the recipe feature work?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: Our app includes a vast collection of recipes for home cooking. You can search by ingredient, cuisine type, or difficulty level. Each recipe comes with step-by-step instructions, nutritional information, and the option to create a shopping list for ingredients.
